title: Macron gets credit for soaring French job market
text:
Macron gets credit for soaring French job market 2:47pm GMT - 02:02 
France's unemployment rate fell below 9 percent for the first time since 2009, registering a sharp drop that is likely to boost President Emmanuel Macron's efforts to reform the country's economy. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
